layout.text: GinnyMae Vintage was created by Jen Dangro. Today it is owned and operated by Jen and her Mom, Emily. Their love for fashion and desire to uniquely style each and every outfit, led to creating their own boutique. GMV is personally curated vintage and sustainable fashion, each piece handpicked. GinnyMae Vintage is named after Jen's grandmother , Emily's Mom, who was sassy and determined, the same way we hope our pieces make you feel each time you wear them.
